Ports
-----

1. Status

    - Connected Port Status
    - Port Errors
        - InvalidCrcCount
        - InvalidTransmissionWordCount
        - LinkFailureCount
        - LossOfSignalCount
        - LossOfSyncCount

2. Information
    
    - Nothing yet

3. Performance Metrics

    - Read / Write Throughput
    - Read / Write IO/s
    - Number of Port Errors
        - InvalidCrcCount
        - InvalidTransmissionWordCount
        - LinkFailureCount
        - LossOfSignalCount
        - LossOfSyncCount

4. Configurable Thresholds

    - make port online / offline configurable
    - Tresholds on Number of
        - InvalidCrcCount
        - InvalidTransmissionWordCount
        - LinkFailureCount
        - LossOfSignalCount
        - LossOfSyncCount

Virtual Disks
-------------

1. Status

    - disk status (Healthy, Offline, in Reclamation, in Recovery)
    - served status (served / unserved)

2. Information

    - Size
    - Recovery Priority
    - Compression enabled
    - Dedup enabled
    - Encryption enabled
    - Write Through enabled
    - Sector Size

3. Performance Metrics

    - Read / Write Throughput
    - Read / Write IO/s

4. Configurable Thresholds

    - thresholds on 
        - upper write IO
        - upper read io
        - upper read latency
        - upper write latency

    - Expected mapping state (server / not served)
    - Expected path state (Path Down)

